The article is a letter from President Barack Obama to the Speaker of the House of Representatives and the President of the Senate. In the letter, the President designates all funding and contributions from foreign governments for Overseas Contingency Operations/Global War on Terrorism. This designation is in accordance with the Continuing Appropriations and Military Construction, Veterans Affairs, and Related Agencies Appropriations Act, 2017, and Zika Response and Preparedness Act. The President's action is outlined in a memorandum from the Director of the Office of Management and Budget, which is enclosed with the letter.